Map Name: gg_mr_house

Version: 1.0

Created By: Paul '[MalReynolds]' Elliott

Dev Notes: This is based on the old Gungame map called mini house. It's one of the first i had played on and offered a small, simple, fast paced experience, which began my love of Gungame. Can call this a tribute to that map.

Based on mini_house.
